channel.title: Coder needed
channel.description: Looking to earn $30?. First let me explain. First off this is a 1 week project and just need you for 1 week. Out of that whole week, I will be telling you what to add, do, ect. You do need java knowledge, and you have to show me that. Paying info: It will be via paypal. Also the more helpfull you are to me, you get more money, so $20-$30 (most likely $30 if you are helpful). If you are interested please contact me at JohnnySkate805@hotmail.com. Also if you dont have anything nice to say, dont say anything at all.
